snippet.title: Star Fox Conquest - A NEW N64 ROM Hack [REVEAL TRAILER]
snippet.description:
This new ROM hack of Zelda 64 completely transforms the game into a new Star Fox adventure, playable on an actual Nintendo 64 console! Star Fox Conquest follows Fox as he crash lands on a mysterious planet and embarks on an adventure forcing him to travel across the galaxy. 
Check out robotsonn who composed the music for the trailer! https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCOziH_AZiHGqRDGpMyKnxww

Support my work and get access to exclusive content and early previews: https://patreon.com/zel640
